   <body>
      <p>Calculate button enables you to generate a calculation summary and details for the selected schedules.</p>
      <p>To view the calculation summary and details, please perform the following:</p>
      <ol>
         <li>Select the schedule check box as shown in the below image.<fig>
               <image placement="break"
                      width="700"
                      href="../attachments/102432709/107118639.jpg"/>
            </fig>
         </li>
         <li>Click Calculate.<p>Calculation summary and details are generated.</p>
         </li>
      </ol>
      <p>According to the qualification and benefits formula, the calculation is performed for the selected program based on the admin-defined type, and also billing and invoicing are performed for the program based on the admin-defined type.</p>
